org.wso2.transport.http.netty.contract

Interface HttpClientConnectorListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HttpConnectorListener

    public interface HttpClientConnectorListener
extends HttpConnectorListener
    HttpClientConnectorListener is the interface for Http ClientConnector event listeners. This is an extension of HttpConnectorListener contains additional capability which are specific only for HttpClientConnector.

    Implementors of this interface can implement only what they prefer to listen for.
